OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FUS Vice President JD Vance arrived in
OL,7,FHungary on Tuesday to support Prime
OL,8,FMinister Viktor Orban's campaign ahead
OL,9,Fof the general election on Sunday.
OL,11,FHe said on Tuesday he was "here to
OL,12,Fhelp" as Orban, who is a close ally of
OL,13,FDonald Trump, is currently trailing in
OL,14,Fthe polls.
OL,16,FVance will spend two days in Hungary,
OL,17,Fwhere he is expected to hold an
OL,18,Fofficial visit with the long-standing
OL,19,Fprime minister and then later appear
OL,20,Fat one of his campaign rallies.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
