OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FOrban is running for his fifth
OL,7,Fconsecutive term as prime minister but
OL,8,Fhe and his nationalist-populist party
OL,9,Fface their toughest race in two
OL,10,Fdecades as his centre-right contender,
OL,11,FPeter Magyar has charged ahead in the
OL,12,Fpolls.
OL,14,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,15,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,16,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,17,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
