OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775642746
OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FMost independent polls are showing a
OL,7,Fdouble-digit deficit for Orban's party
OL,8,FFidesz among decided voters ahead of
OL,9,Fthe vote on April 12, so the Hungarian
OL,10,Fleader has sought to be seen in public
OL,11,Fwith his international allies to try
OL,12,Fand boost his popularity.
OL,14,FTrump has repeatedly endorsed Orban
OL,15,Ffor re-election and many in the Make
OL,16,FAmerica Great Again movement approve
OL,17,Fof the Hungarian leader's opposition
OL,18,Fto immigration and his government's
OL,19,Fcurtailing of LGBTQ+ rights.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
