OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FCritics have long accused Orban of
OL,7,Ftaking over Hungary's institutions,
OL,8,Fclamping down on press freedom and
OL,9,Foverseeing entrenched political
OL,10,Fcorruption - charges which he denies.
OL,12,FVance and his wife, Usha, were
OL,13,Fwelcomed at the airport in Budapest by
OL,14,FHungary's Foreign Minister Peter
OL,15,FSzijjarto.
OL,17,FThe two men greeted each other warmly,
OL,18,Fand Szijjarto presented Usha Vance
OL,19,Fwith a bouquet of flowers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
