CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775642746
OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FSzijjarto told state media that Vance
OL,7,Fis the first US vice president to
OL,8,Fvisit Hungary since 1991, and he is
OL,9,Fthe highest-ranking US official in the
OL,10,Fcountry since 2006.
OL,12,FMagyar, who has pledged to bring
OL,13,FHungary back towards its Western
OL,14,Fpartners and end its drift towards
OL,15,FMoscow, gave a pointed critique of
OL,16,FVance's visit in social media posts on
OL,17,FTuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/8
