PN,30906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F309A1775642746
OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,F"No foreign country may interfere in
OL,7,FHungarian elections. This is our
OL,8,Fcountry," Magyar wrote. "Hungarian
OL,9,Fhistory is not written in Washington,
OL,10,FMoscow, or Brussels - it is written in
OL,11,FHungary's streets and squares."
OL,13,F"I respectfully ask the US Vice
OL,14,FPresident, who is coming to Hungary,
OL,15,Fthat if he is already campaigning for
OL,16,FViktor Orban, the Hungarian people
OL,17,Fshould not pay the price," Magyar said.
OL,19,FThe visit is not the first sign of
OL,20,Fsupport for Orban by the current US
OL,21,Fadministration.
