OL,3,CJD Vance arrives in Hungary 'to help'
OL,4,Cwith upcoming election
OL,6,FHungary, which was one of few European
OL,7,Fcountries to refuse to assist Ukraine
OL,8,Fwith financial assistance or weapons
OL,9,Fto ward off Russia's full-scale
OL,10,Finvasion, has remained firmly
OL,11,Fcommitted to purchasing Russian energy
OL,12,Fdespite EU efforts to move away from
OL,13,Fthose supplies.
OL,15,FIn November, Hungary received an
OL,16,Fexemption from US sanctions on Russian
OL,17,Foil and gas after a White House
OL,18,Fmeeting between Orban and Trump.
